  (str actYear) (str 1957)
  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Home Affairs`)
  (str department) (str `Department of Home`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to make in pursuance of clause (3) of article 16 of the Constitution special provisions for requirement as to residence in regard to certain classes of public employment in certain areas and to repeal existing laws prescribing any such requirement.`)
  (str enforcementDate) (str 21-3-1957)
  (str notification) (str `21st March, 1957, vide notification No. G.S.R. 2323, dated 21st March, 1959, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i).`)
